904
00:49:29.040 --> 00:49:29.840
Hang it. Neil.

905
00:49:30.060 --> 00:49:32.040
If you see the sheriff. you stop him.

906
00:49:32.180 --> 00:49:32.680
He knows.

907
00:49:33.040 --> 00:49:33.180
Shit.

908
00:49:41.620 --> 00:49:46.690
Calm down. Mary Beth.

909
00:49:48.250 --> 00:49:50.070
We don't want to hurt you.

910
00:49:50.490 --> 00:49:52.050
Sure you don't.

911
00:49:52.770 --> 00:49:54.370
I wasn't born yesterday.

912
00:50:18.000 --> 00:50:20.600
He got no fucking respect.

913
00:50:22.160 --> 00:50:22.520
Okay.

914
00:50:46.560 --> 00:50:47.720
Suck on this.

915
00:51:09.102 --> 00:51:10.848
Let there be light.

916
00:51:14.419 --> 00:51:16.551
You don't understand.

917
00:51:16.551 --> 00:51:26.207
Come on !

918
00:51:34.950 --> 00:51:35.590
Good evening. everybody.

919
